02:00:46,503 --> 02:00:49,587
Johnny, run to Metacomet's place by the river.

1351
02:00:51,299 --> 02:00:55,247
Tell him to come and save his people. Run, man!

1352
02:00:58,971 --> 02:01:00,299
Here come the witches!

1353
02:01:03,599 --> 02:01:05,556
Open the cell.

1354
02:01:17,111 --> 02:01:19,482
- Never mind the child. - Pearl!

1355
02:01:19,946 --> 02:01:21,404
- Get in, woman! - Pearl?

1356
02:01:22,072 --> 02:01:23,863
Worry not, Mistress.

1357
02:01:24,074 --> 02:01:26,362
I'll see she's raised up to fear the Lord.

1358
02:01:45,590 --> 02:01:47,547
Open up, murderer!

1359
02:02:17,532 --> 02:02:20,069
There is no witchcraft here!

1360
02:02:22,411 --> 02:02:24,652
If we hang these women,

1361
02:02:25,246 --> 02:02:27,368
then what have we become?

1362
02:02:28,374 --> 02:02:29,536
Who are we

1363
02:02:29,875 --> 02:02:31,037
to condemn

1364
02:02:31,335 --> 02:02:33,291
on God's behalf?

1365
02:02:42,092 --> 02:02:44,878
I love this woman.

1366
02:02:48,221 --> 02:02:48,756
I am

1367
02:02:50,474 --> 02:02:52,799
the father of her child.

1368
02:02:53,434 --> 02:02:54,762
And in God's eyes,

1369
02:02:55,895 --> 02:02:57,602
I am her husband.

1370
02:03:06,069 --> 02:03:09,521
If you must hang someone,

1371
02:03:10,740 --> 02:03:12,115
to appease

1372
02:03:12,783 --> 02:03:15,949
your anger and fear,

1373
02:03:18,579 --> 02:03:19,954
then hang me.

1374
02:04:01,779 --> 02:04:02,693
Hang him!

1375
02:04:04,073 --> 02:04:06,065
Hang him! Hang him!

1376
02:04:06,449 --> 02:04:07,279
Hang him!

1377
02:05:06,871 --> 02:05:08,448
Bastards!

1378
02:05:49,987 --> 02:05:51,149
Hester!

1379
02:05:56,827 --> 02:05:58,107
Where's my daughter, Pearl?

1380
02:05:58,411 --> 02:05:59,822
She's in the meeting house!

1381
02:06:30,935 --> 02:06:34,553
You are free, my people. Go back to Metacomet!

1382
02:06:35,189 --> 02:06:36,564
Go back to the forest!

1383
02:07:51,790 --> 02:07:55,918
Bellingham will do anything to conceal this madness from England.

1384
02:07:57,670 --> 02:08:00,421
He has sworn to me that he will remove the letter.

1385
02:08:01,673 --> 02:08:03,961
And make thee a public apology.

1386
02:08:07,719 --> 02:08:09,841
How close they are, love and hate.

1387
02:08:11,138 --> 02:08:13,843
We're no less bound by one than the other.

1388
02:08:18,561 --> 02:08:20,683
Rest in peace, Roger Prynne.

1389
02:08:30,736 --> 02:08:33,108
This letter has served a purpose.

1390
02:08:33,989 --> 02:08:34,855
Though not the one

1391
02:08:35,115 --> 02:08:36,443
they had intended.

1392
02:08:37,951 --> 02:08:39,990
So why would I stay here?

1393
02:08:40,327 --> 02:08:44,277
To be accepted by them? To be tamed by them?

1394
02:08:51,795 --> 02:08:55,080
- There is no perfect world. - No, not perfect.

1395
02:08:57,216 --> 02:08:59,422
But we came here to make a new one.

1396
02:09:02,762 --> 02:09:04,303
And for Pearl's sake,

1397
02:09:07,140 --> 02:09:08,598
I must do just that.

1398
02:09:13,144 --> 02:09:14,093
Hester.

1399
02:09:18,440 --> 02:09:19,436
Hester!

1400
02:09:21,609 --> 02:09:22,807
Look at me.

1401
02:09:25,529 --> 02:09:27,402
If I look at you, I won't be able to leave

1402
02:09:27,655 --> 02:09:28,818
Then leave.

1403
02:09:30,282 --> 02:09:31,740
Brave the wilds!

1404
02:09:38,998 --> 02:09:40,278
But Hester,

1405
02:09:41,459 --> 02:09:44,992
I'm not letting you go without me.

1406
02:09:57,554 --> 02:09:58,882
They're watching us.

1407
02:10:23,574 --> 02:10:25,945
In the faraway Carolinas,

1408
02:10:26,576 --> 02:10:29,446
they were at last to find a measure ofthe happiness

1409
02:10:29,703 --> 02:10:32,454
that hade been denied them forso long.

1410
02:10:33,539 --> 02:10:36,410
My fatherdied before I reached my teens.

1411
02:10:37,168 --> 02:10:39,326
Some say that was a punishment.

1412
02:10:40,838 --> 02:10:44,171
My motherneverremarried norloved another.

1413
02:10:44,966 --> 02:10:47,124
Some say that was a punishment.

1414
02:10:48,302 --> 02:10:49,416
As forme,

1415
02:10:50,803 --> 02:10:52,677
I do not see it that way.

1416
02:10:53,514 --> 02:10:55,839
Myparents shared a love like no other.

1417
02:10:56,892 --> 02:11:00,058
I know the spirit ofthat love lives within me.

1418
02:11:00,603 --> 02:11:02,974
And will live within my children forever.

1419
02:11:05,940 --> 02:11:10,316
Who is to say what is a sin in God's eyes?


